Use python from venv. If there is no venv - use `pnpm run init-python` to create venv.
Use `pnpm t` to run tests. Do not add comments to tests. Try to keep them concise.
Use `pnpm run lint` to check for linting errors and `pnpm run lint --fix` to fix some of them.
